   Scratch To Win!
   [spacer.gif] [corner.gif]
   Scratcher
   California Lottery® Scratchers® are easy to play and you could win on
   the spot! You can buy Scratchers only at California Lottery retailers.
   There are a variety of different Scratchers to choose from, each with
   its own theme and playstyle.
   Use the pulldown menu to the right to see each game, or click on the
   Scratchers Gallery to see a small thumbnail of each game.
   After game start, some prizes, including top prizes may have been
   claimed. For information on the number of top prizes remaining in
   current Scratchers games, please call 1-800-LOTTERY and press 1-3 on
   your touch tone phone.
